Minister Calderone spoke of "a truly immense tragedy, of which it is still difficult to define complex and the dynamics of the facts: I think it's hard to express, because you risk falling into rhetoric," said Calderone." Not only a duty visit, but also "the proximity of the government to the territory and communities that are very proven, because this is a plant that is also very linked to this territory". For Calderone, now "we have respect to the work of rescuers and pollutants and families" but attention must return to the issue of safety at work.
&nbsp;
"We really need to invest in a culture of security that must be a culture of life, which must be of each of us, because taking care of our lives means to have care and respect also of the lives of others and this is a fundamental element." "The rules are there, we are putting in the field of new ones, we have launched recently - said the minister - we are also aware that there are situations in which there are also improper uses of some types and contracts of work and these things must be rightly sanctioned and above all also identified the tools in order to prevent accidents again based on this".
<h2>Enel Green Power: "There is no need to talk about causes"</h2>
For the ad of Enel Green Powe>r,&nbsp;Saveer Bernabei, who is following the research of the missing, "it is not appropriate to talk about causes, it is a complex situation". "The most important thing is to help families and help firefighters to recover survivors. We are collaborating with the authorities," added the manager, explaining that&nbsp; "the work in progress was technological update and we were carrying out testing tests on the second group. The first had already been realized in the past weeks and had ended." &nbsp;
&nbsp;
"The work began in September 2022 according to a programmed activity that was ending in these days with contractors among the most prestigious companies in the world," said Bernabei, who mentioned among others the name of Siemens, "the contractors can turn to other specialists, because here the works can only be done by specialists".
